text:
Had a typo in my config and received this error message:

apache2: Syntax error on line 173 of /etc/apache2/httpd.conf: Syntax error on line 61 of /etc/apache2/vhosts.d/00_default_vhost.conf: Expected </VirutalHost> but saw </VirtualHost>

"Expected" and "but saw" values should be exchanged.
creator: christian.pontesegger@web.de

text: At this point it's checking that the sections are balanced, so it "expects" to see the same typo on the closing tag.
creator: covener@gmail.com
